The paper deals with blind image quality assessment, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves learning to rank, which is a machine learning technique that falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of multiple kernel learning, which is a popular technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
